title: adding project created in idea
message:
adding project created in idea

it contains 4 modules:
  - wallpaper - the code needed in walpaper service,
  - gfx - open gl shared code
  - demo - the project which can be used to quickly test new code
  - sun - "Your very own Sun" live wallpaper
